    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Strandesia martensi n. sp. A. carapace, right lateral view; B. carapace, left lateral view; C. carapace, dorsal view; D. valve surface of A.; E. muscle scars of G.; F. LV, internal view; G. RV, internal view. Scale bar = 100 Μm for A – C, F – G; = 16 Μm for D; 40 Μm for E. Arrow points toward the anterior end." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/253765/files/figure.png" ;
